To compile `make all`
Controls:
	* s -> rotate shoulder anticlockwise
	* S -> rotate shoulder clockwise
	* e -> rotate elbow anticlockwise
	* E -> rotate elbow clockwise
	* q -> rotate finger 1 anticlockwise
	* Q -> rotate finger 1 clockwise
	* w -> rotate finger 2 anticlockwise
	* W -> rotate finger 2 clockwise
	* r -> reset scene
	* a -> play animation
	* p -> if object is not visible then it becomes visible otherwise it becomes invisible
